reviews.text: Came here on a Saturday afternoon to happily find some seats available. Quiet environment. I wish more Starbucks were like this so people can enjoy their coffee and focus on their work!
Friendly staff. Clean and neat at all times.
Best Starbucks service I received in Hong Kong. Friendly and warm baristas made my wife and I come back to this location multiple times for our coffee breaks.
Most food different from Singapore. Suggest they rotate food from different countries outlets
I like the calmer less hectic pace of this shop, muted light and good place to hide and relax for a while

result.name: 星巴克

reviews.text:
下午兩點多進到來，大部分的無人座位上都是才未回收的垃圾，店裡地板上也有散落紙巾垃圾。
櫃面有2個店員，没有排隊的非繁忙時段，但也未見店員去稍微清理環境。不自律的客人加上不自覺又不自動的店員，就成為了我在香港看過的最髒的星巴客！

清潔系大問題. 
主要倚賴客人自律, 離開時將杯碟放入垃圾筒, 但有時客人唔做, 枱面就要很久才有人清潔.
其次系垃圾筒細咗啲, 常滿咁囉.
和其他星巴克一樣: 乾淨,整潔,有叉電位。
環境舒適，享受咖啡好去處！
Came here on a Saturday afternoon to happily find some seats available. Quiet environment. I wish more Starbucks were like this so people can enjoy their coffee and focus on their work!
